text: Shristi Shrestha ( (born October 18, 1989) in Chitwan, Nepal is a Nepali actress, model and the title winner of Miss Nepal 2012.Shristi Shrestha gets crowned as Miss Nepal 2012 . Globalbeauties.com (May 2012). Retrieved on 2012-05-25. She won Miss Nepal title, beating 16 other contestants of Miss Nepal 2012 beauty pageant. Shristi Shrestha is Miss Nepal 2012! . Nepaliblogger.com (2012-05-07). Retrieved on 2012-08-01. She also represented Nepal in Miss World 2012 in China. She won Public Choice Award in Miss World 2012 & also selected in Top 10 Dancers. She is famous Nepali celebrity and rose fame from her debut moive Gajalu which was superhit in Nepal. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1989 births Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Miss Nepal winners Category:Nepalese movie actors Category:Living people Category:Nepalese models
